rComments: Good course. A lot of homework but not that tricky. Good exposure. Must take at undergraduate level.

Prof. Gao is an amazing Professor. She is very helpful and patient towards all her students. I took this course in Fall 2013 with her. She explains all the concepts very clearly and interactively. She also motivates all her students to think outside the box. I would highly recommend students to take this course with her.
